headline: Federal Realty Completes $170 Million in Asset Dispositions as Part of Capital Recycling Strategy
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE: FRT) today announced the completion of the sale of two assets for combined proceeds of approximately $170 million, consistent with the company's long-term strategy to recycle capital into high-quality and high-growth opportunities.
